                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                        <p><strong>Name:</strong> Not Provided</p>
                        <p><strong>Country:</strong>  Not Provided</p>
                        <p><strong>State:</strong> Not Provided</p>
                        <p><strong>City:</strong> Not Provided</p>
